Package: Phydon
Type: Package
Title: Estimate maximum growth rates of bacteria species
Version: 1.1.0
Author: Liang Xu
Maintainer: Liang Xu <xl0418@gmail.com>
Description: Phydon is a package that estimates the maximum growth rates of bacteria species based on their genomic features. It takes advantage of the mechanisitic method "gRodon" and the phylogenetic signal to provide a more accurate estimation of the maximum growth rates of bacteria species.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: ape,castor,gRodon,Biostrings,picante,stats,utils
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
